	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Tormenter wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Will the 70ns chips work for NES games?  Since its a faster chip, it will slow down to the speed it needs for the game, correct?</div>
<br />I wouldn't say "slow down" so much as "have the requested data ready long before the NES needs it"... <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
